items.name: M3U8-Downloader-With-Authorization
items.description: This is a simple Python-based GUI tool for downloading videos from M3U8 URLs, including those with authentication parameters after ?. It uses ffmpeg to handle the downloading process and ensures that the entire URL, including query parameters, is preserved for proper access.
